overview: Just when you thought he was winding down, Everything is Terrible!'s Dante Fontana winds YOU back up with another dazzling, well-curated, mix DVD of random goodness. Like it? Love it? No, trust us when we say you gotta have this in your DVD player (or streaming device) in time for the holidays alongside a cookie and a warm glass of milk. Season freaklings!
title: Dante's Mystery Mix Volume 6
